                                  %br
                                  %p{:style => "margin: 10px 0;padding: 0;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #202020;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;"} I'd really appreciate it if you took a few moments to complete this quick user experience survey.
